Dialogue: 10,0:00:01.96,0:00:03.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nokker itu
Dialogue: 10,0:00:04.00,0:00:06.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,muncul di hadapan Fushi
Dialogue: 10,0:00:07.00,0:00:09.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan menantangnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:11.47,0:00:14.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo, aku akan bermain denganmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:18.26,0:00:19.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku harus kembali.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:19.18,0:00:20.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hore! Aku bebas!
Dialogue: 10,0:00:22.56,0:00:24.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bolehkah aku menemuimu lagi?
Dialogue: 10,0:00:24.27,0:00:25.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku suka bersenang-senang.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:25.69,0:00:27.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Orang itu juga akan bahagia.
Dialogue: 10,0:00:27.90,0:00:29.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Orang itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:04.75,0:02:06.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Saat menyusuri jalan,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:06.41,0:02:10.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku yakin akan bertemu Fushi...
Dialogue: 10,0:02:10.79,0:02:12.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang harus kulakukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:12.50,0:02:15.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan ke rumah Yuki dan melihatnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:15.84,0:02:17.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi
Dialogue: 10,0:02:17.59,0:02:20.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,alasan apa yang harus kupakai?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:21.18,0:02:23.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Fushi, sini kubereskan PR-mu"?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:23.97,0:02:25.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu terlalu agresif, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:25.68,0:02:28.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tonari pasti bakal sinis melihatku.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:28.98,0:02:31.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Kamu ingkar janji buat menemani aku\Npulang sekolah tiap hari."
Dialogue: 10,0:02:31.81,0:02:32.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Kamu jahat banget!"
Dialogue: 10,0:02:32.90,0:02:33.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:33.94,0:02:36.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cewek yang terlalu baperan\Nbakal dibenci.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:36.99,0:02:39.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Yuki, aku menemukan batu berkilau."
Dialogue: 10,0:02:39.66,0:02:40.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Apa itu Power Stone?"
Dialogue: 10,0:02:40.99,0:02:42.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Wah, Senior hebat!"
Dialogue: 10,0:02:42.41,0:02:43.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nah, itu dia.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:47.00,0:02:50.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi mungkin dia lagi tidak di rumah.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:50.83,0:02:52.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Haruskah aku mengintip dulu?
Dialogue: 10,0:02:52.71,0:02:54.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kayak penguntit saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:02:55.50,0:02:56.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Omong-omong,
Dialogue: 10,0:02:56.88,0:03:00.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,apa dia tidak cemas\Nmeninggalkanku sendirian?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:01.18,0:03:03.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Atau dia sudah tidak peduli lagi?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:04.35,0:03:07.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang harus kubilang\Nkalau ketemu dia nanti?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:11.14,0:03:13.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak bisa berhenti memikirkan Fushi.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:13.90,0:03:15.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku merasa bodoh banget.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:16.15,0:03:18.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kok aku malah galau soal cinta, sih?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:18.94,0:03:21.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku punya ibu yang baik sekarang,
Dialogue: 10,0:03:21.24,0:03:22.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan teman dekat juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:22.91,0:03:24.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sudah bahagia.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:24.74,0:03:25.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi
Dialogue: 10,0:03:27.66,0:03:33.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,kalau Fushi bilang dia mencintaiku,\Nsemuanya pasti jadi sempurna.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:34.71,0:03:35.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Penyu.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:37.42,0:03:38.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fushi?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:38.80,0:03:41.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tolong ajari aku apa itu cinta.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:43.43,0:03:45.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak disangka bisa ketemu di sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:47.93,0:03:49.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini takdir.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:49.22,0:03:51.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, ini pasti takdir.
Dialogue: 10,0:03:53.35,0:03:54.23,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fushi?
Dialogue: 10,0:03:54.31,0:03:56.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa? Bertahanlah!
Dialogue: 10,0:03:57.61,0:03:58.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia masih hidup!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:01.61,0:04:03.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bikin kaget saja!
Dialogue: 10,0:04:03.99,0:04:05.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fushi, bagaimana keadaanmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:05.82,0:04:06.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu sudah tidak apa-apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:07.08,0:04:09.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, maaf sudah bikin khawatir.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:10.20,0:04:11.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Syukurlah.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:11.75,0:04:13.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begini…
Dialogue: 10,0:04:13.21,0:04:16.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ajak aku jalan hari Minggu nanti.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:17.00,0:04:18.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ke mana?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:18.21,0:04:19.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ke mana saja boleh.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:21.01,0:04:24.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu sudah janji menemaniku\Nsepulang sekolah, tapi malah kabur.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:24.68,0:04:27.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku maafkan,\Nasal kamu mau kencan sama aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:27.43,0:04:29.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kencan?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:29.10,0:04:31.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa itu kencan?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:31.10,0:04:32.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayolah…
Dialogue: 10,0:04:32.89,0:04:34.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan lupakan "kencan" kita.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:34.73,0:04:37.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu kode rencana tempur kita\Nbuat kalahkan Nokker dan selamatkan Bumi.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:37.61,0:04:38.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tentu saja bukan.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:38.90,0:04:41.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu sebabnya aku berencana pergi sekarang.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:41.15,0:04:42.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mizuha, aku mengerti.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:42.61,0:04:44.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan berkencan denganmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:44.95,0:04:48.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Setelah ini berakhir, kau harus memaafkanku\N karena pergi sendirian.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:49.70,0:04:52.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cara bicaranya tidak enak banget.
Dialogue: 10,0:04:52.75,0:04:54.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita ketemu pukul 10.00 hari Minggu
Dialogue: 10,0:04:54.75,0:04:56.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,di depan stasiun, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:04:58.71,0:05:00.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dasar anak muda.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:00.50,0:05:03.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa mereka akan mulai\Nberkencan seperti ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:03.88,0:05:05.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau membohongi kami!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:06.01,0:05:07.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kedamaian apanya?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:07.39,0:05:09.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nokker itu mengambil tubuhku!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:09.47,0:05:12.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia mengayunkan pemotong rumput liar\Nsecara membabi buta!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:12.35,0:05:13.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa ada masalah?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:14.06,0:05:16.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tidak mencemaskanku?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:16.10,0:05:17.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau kepalaku putus, aku mati!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:17.69,0:05:18.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:19.90,0:05:21.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fushi, kau akan mati?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:21.15,0:05:22.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lebih tepatnya,
Dialogue: 10,0:05:22.73,0:05:25.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku tak akan bisa berubah\Nmenjadi wujud ini lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:25.20,0:05:27.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, aku harus membasmi semua Nokker.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:28.03,0:05:29.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita harus habisi mereka!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:30.03,0:05:34.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika menurutmu gadis itu ancaman,\Nhadapi dia sendiri.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:34.58,0:05:37.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak bisa mengabulkan keinginanmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:37.21,0:05:39.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Harus bisa!
Dialogue: 10,0:05:39.33,0:05:43.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Pertama, tarik kembali kebohonganmu\Nsoal dunia sudah damai.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:43.21,0:05:44.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lalu bantu aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:44.55,0:05:47.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau masih punya kekuatan\Nuntuk melacak Nokker, kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:05:47.80,0:05:50.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kekuatanku sudah hampir habis.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:50.55,0:05:53.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hingga kini, aku menganggap tanah\Nsebagai tubuhku sendiri.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:53.18,0:05:55.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitulah caraku melacak Nokker,\Nmakhluk asing itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:55.73,0:05:57.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi aku tidak bisa melakukannya lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:05:57.19,0:06:00.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena aku memberimu kemampuan\Nuntuk terhubung kembali.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:01.02,0:06:04.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku hanya bisa ikut campur\Ndengan orang-orang di sekitarku
Dialogue: 10,0:06:04.65,0:06:06.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan merasakan ketidakharmonisan\Ndi dalam diri mereka.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:06.86,0:06:09.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, begitulah caramu menemukan Mimori.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:09.41,0:06:11.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kekuatan ini juga perlahan memudar.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:11.95,0:06:14.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lagi pula, aku tak berbohong.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:14.16,0:06:17.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dunia sedang dalam kondisi terbaiknya.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:17.96,0:06:19.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:19.29,0:06:21.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,usaha mati-matian Fushi hari ini\Nmungkin percuma.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:21.50,0:06:22.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Satoru.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:23.00,0:06:25.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa mereka teman-temanmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:27.84,0:06:29.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di mana kamu ketemu mereka?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:30.01,0:06:30.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di taman.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:31.68,0:06:34.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku Sumika dari panti asuhan.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:34.64,0:06:36.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku kakak tertua di panti,
Dialogue: 10,0:06:36.18,0:06:38.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,sekaligus walinya bocah ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:38.27,0:06:41.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Omong-omong,\Naku yang terkuat di panti asuhan.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:41.15,0:06:43.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Asal tahu saja,\Naku pernah bikin menangis bocah di sekolah.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:43.65,0:06:44.65,dialog,,0,0,0,,Senang bertemu.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:44.73,0:06:45.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Salam kenal.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:45.94,0:06:49.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku Yuki.\NAku suka tempat energi dan OOPArts.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:50.03,0:06:51.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalian di sana rupanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:51.20,0:06:53.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fushi, sini. Kita bicara di luar.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:53.41,0:06:54.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Halo.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:54.74,0:06:55.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa kau?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:55.66,0:06:56.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenalan kami.
Dialogue: 10,0:06:57.00,0:06:59.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau juga ikut? Kamu bakal baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 10,0:06:59.58,0:07:01.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan cemaskan aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:01.71,0:07:04.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Astaga, kau membuatku takut.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:04.46,0:07:08.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak disangka kau diserang\NMimori palsu di sekolah.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:08.09,0:07:12.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mimori memintaku menyampaikan ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:12.89,0:07:16.27,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Tak usah coba mengalahkan Nokker itu lagi."
Dialogue: 10,0:07:16.35,0:07:17.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa? Apa alasannya?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:18.02,0:07:20.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia tidak mau memberitahuku.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:20.44,0:07:23.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Memangnya tidak apa-apa\Nkalau tubuhnya terus diambil alih?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:24.15,0:07:26.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cuma itu yang dia katakan.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:27.11,0:07:28.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terus aku harus bagaimana?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:28.49,0:07:30.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Haruskah aku diam saja?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:30.32,0:07:32.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Makhluk itu bilang\Ndia akan mendatangiku lagi.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:34.58,0:07:38.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia juga bilang,\N"Orang itu juga akan bahagia."
Dialogue: 10,0:07:38.29,0:07:41.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Orang itu"? Siapa yang dia maksud?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:41.54,0:07:43.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tahu sesuatu tidak, Bocah Hitam?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:45.71,0:07:47.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia fokus banget sama PR-nya.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:47.30,0:07:48.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar juga.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:48.21,0:07:50.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa tidak suruh Nixon dan yang lain\Nmengikuti Mimori palsu?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:50.84,0:07:52.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka mungkin bisa cari tahu\Nsiapa "orang itu".
Dialogue: 10,0:07:53.76,0:07:54.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami?
Dialogue: 10,0:07:55.01,0:07:56.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu ide bagus.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:56.60,0:07:57.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo kita lakukan.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:57.89,0:07:59.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu.
Dialogue: 10,0:07:59.60,0:08:02.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nokker yang merasuki tubuh Mimori\Nsangat agresif.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:02.85,0:08:06.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika ketahuan,\Ndia tak akan ragu memulai pertarungan.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:06.23,0:08:07.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita singkirkan para keroco dulu,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:07.82,0:08:09.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,lalu cari tahu kelemahannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:09.40,0:08:10.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Tapi…\N- Bon.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:10.86,0:08:14.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Anak itu seharusnya bisa merasakan\Nkeberadaan Nokker.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:14.49,0:08:16.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu salah satu caranya.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:16.20,0:08:18.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi apa pun yang dilakukan,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:18.12,0:08:20.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mimori palsu pasti akan bertindak.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:20.20,0:08:21.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kata Bu Izumi?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:21.91,0:08:24.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fushi, selagi kami menyelidiki\Npergerakan Mimori,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:24.33,0:08:25.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,bersiaplah untuk kemungkinan serangan
Dialogue: 10,0:08:26.00,0:08:27.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan bekerja sama dengan Bocah Hitam
Dialogue: 10,0:08:27.34,0:08:29.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,untuk mencari manusia\Nyang dirasuki Nokker.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:29.84,0:08:32.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau ketemu,\Napa kita akan menghancurkan mereka?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:32.72,0:08:34.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka adalah makhluk abadi.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:34.18,0:08:36.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika memisahkan kesadaran mereka\Ndari tubuhnya,
Dialogue: 10,0:08:36.39,0:08:38.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nokker mungkin akan kehilangan\Ntempat berlindung.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:39.31,0:08:41.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Incar di sini, di batang otak.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:41.60,0:08:43.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lalu kau bisa menghabisinya\Ndalam satu pukulan.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:43.10,0:08:46.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bu Izumi bilang jika menyerang kepalanya,\Nkau bisa membunuh Nokker.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:46.65,0:08:50.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tusuk atau tebas, terserah kau saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:51.44,0:08:52.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fushi.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:53.20,0:08:56.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah, aku bisa melakukannya.\NAku bisa membunuhnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:08:56.28,0:08:57.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:08:57.70,0:09:00.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bukankah selama ini\Nkau mengalahkan Nokker?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:00.58,0:09:03.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Karena makhluk itu bisa merasakan sakit.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:04.25,0:09:06.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dulu tidak begini.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:06.29,0:09:08.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi sekarang,\Nrasa sakitnya terasa begitu nyata.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:08.29,0:09:11.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka merasakan sakit\Nyang sama seperti kita.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:11.21,0:09:14.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rasa sakit terkena pisau itu mengerikan.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:14.09,0:09:16.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana kalau pakai racun\Natau bom saja?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:16.80,0:09:19.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tahu ini sulit bagimu, Fushi.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:19.85,0:09:21.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi yang kau rasakan hanya sesaat.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:21.77,0:09:25.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak… Ya, kau benar.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:25.89,0:09:27.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu bukan masalah.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:27.81,0:09:31.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf, tapi aku mengutamakan\Nhidupku sendiri.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:31.44,0:09:34.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan berasumsi aku akan membantumu.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:34.74,0:09:36.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hentikan itu!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:36.45,0:09:38.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Entah apa yang terjadi padamu,
Dialogue: 10,0:09:38.12,0:09:40.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi dari yang kulihat,\Nkau yang memulai semua ini!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:41.41,0:09:42.33,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fushi!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:42.41,0:09:44.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan lakukan itu! Tenanglah!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:45.33,0:09:46.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:47.33,0:09:49.04,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fushi, minta maaf!
Dialogue: 10,0:09:53.13,0:09:53.96,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku mau pulang.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.05,0:09:54.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kuantar kau pulang.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:54.97,0:09:56.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Tidak usah.\N- Ayolah, jangan begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:09:56.97,0:09:58.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mau bergandengan?
Dialogue: 10,0:09:59.60,0:10:01.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia lupa lembar tugas Matematikanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:03.31,0:10:06.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jawabannya salah,\Npadahal tampangnya pintar.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:06.60,0:10:10.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu aneh. \NBocah Hitam harusnya jago Matematika.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:10.77,0:10:11.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benarkah?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:12.36,0:10:14.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Inikah yang dia maksud tadi,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:14.40,0:10:17.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Saat pembuluh darah berubah,\Njantung juga berubah"?
Dialogue: 10,0:10:17.65,0:10:20.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, dia jadi lebih muda\Ndan otaknya juga mengecil.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:22.20,0:10:25.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu,\Njika Nokker mendapatkan tubuh baru,
Dialogue: 10,0:10:25.29,0:10:28.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,mungkin hati mereka menjadi baik.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:28.62,0:10:30.63,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kuharap begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:30.71,0:10:34.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menangislah! Berteriaklah!\NDasar babi gemuk!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:34.96,0:10:37.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Beraninya kau memata-mataiku!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:37.51,0:10:42.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau kau berani bilang ke orang lain,\Naku akan bikin kau lebih menderita.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:42.80,0:10:44.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Jawab!\N- Ya!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:44.18,0:10:45.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Salah jawabannya!\N- Pekik…
Dialogue: 10,0:10:45.93,0:10:47.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terus berteriak!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:47.89,0:10:48.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lebih keras!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:52.61,0:10:54.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fushi, maafkan aku!
Dialogue: 10,0:10:54.98,0:10:57.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku bangun kesiangan.
Dialogue: 10,0:10:58.36,0:11:00.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kelamaan menunggu, ya? Maaf.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:00.20,0:11:02.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku telat di kencan pertama kita.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:02.99,0:11:04.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau begitu, ayo.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:04.74,0:11:05.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita mau ke mana?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:06.04,0:11:07.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Coba kupikir.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:07.75,0:11:09.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa dia lagi cosplay?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:09.08,0:11:10.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bajunya aneh banget.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:11.33,0:11:13.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ingin belanja baju.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:16.38,0:11:18.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kamu tidak masuk sekolah belakangan ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:18.80,0:11:20.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada kejadian sesuatu?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:20.80,0:11:24.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tonari bilang kamu juga tidak pulang.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:26.39,0:11:29.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak mau ada yang melihatku\Ndalam kondisi lemah.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:29.98,0:11:32.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sejak diserang oleh Mimori Nokker,
Dialogue: 10,0:11:32.44,0:11:34.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku tidur di luar,\Nbersiap menghadapi serangan
Dialogue: 10,0:11:34.19,0:11:35.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,yang bisa datang kapan saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:36.23,0:11:40.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi Mimori yang asli bilang tidak apa-apa\Nkalau aku tidak melawan.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:40.57,0:11:42.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bocah Hitam juga tak akan membantuku.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:42.87,0:11:44.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang terjadi sekarang?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:45.08,0:11:49.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tentu saja,\Ndunia ini tidak membutuhkan Nokker.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:50.79,0:11:52.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, memang ada sesuatu.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:53.33,0:11:55.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cerita, dong.
Dialogue: 10,0:11:55.54,0:11:58.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak perlu. Kau sudah memilih pakaianmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:11:58.21,0:12:00.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fushi, coba ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:01.47,0:12:03.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, kau mencarikan baju untukku.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:03.68,0:12:06.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi benarkah tidak apa-apa\Nkau membelikanku baju?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:06.26,0:12:09.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak apa-apa.\NIbu memberiku uang saku.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:10.48,0:12:13.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Omong-omong, apa ada masalah dengan ibumu?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:14.31,0:12:16.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia baik banget sama aku.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:16.19,0:12:18.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hari-hari kami sangat damai\Nsampai aku kaget sendiri.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:18.82,0:12:19.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Begitu rupanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:20.40,0:12:21.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Syukurlah.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:24.20,0:12:28.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak.\NAku yang tidak boleh lupa.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:28.87,0:12:31.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini bukan kedamaian.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:32.21,0:12:37.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Nokker pasti punya motif\Nuntuk mengendalikan tubuh manusia.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:39.51,0:12:40.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fushi, kau sadar, tidak?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:41.59,0:12:42.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sadar apa?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:43.26,0:12:45.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Para cewek memperhatikanmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:45.89,0:12:48.18,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mereka semua berpikir kau keren.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:48.26,0:12:49.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Keren?
Dialogue: 10,0:12:49.60,0:12:51.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau cocok di kota ini sekarang.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:51.52,0:12:53.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau harus selalu berpakaian seperti ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:55.19,0:12:57.69,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di sana kau rupanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:12:58.11,0:13:00.11,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa maumu, Nona?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:00.19,0:13:02.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak disangka kau masih memikirkan kencan.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:02.99,0:13:05.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan harap aku melepaskanmu\Nsetelah kejadian waktu itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:05.78,0:13:06.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa sebelumnya?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:06.70,0:13:07.87,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau mengenalnya?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:07.95,0:13:10.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau menyakiti Satoru, kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:10.62,0:13:12.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan bilang kau lupa!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:13.04,0:13:14.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Satoru?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:15.71,0:13:18.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau… Bu Sumika?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:19.46,0:13:21.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak sengaja melakukannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:21.46,0:13:23.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu, dia terluka?
Dialogue: 10,0:13:24.01,0:13:26.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak usah pura-pura bego!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:26.13,0:13:28.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kepalanya benjol\Ndan badannya lecet-lecet.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:28.89,0:13:30.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,Satoru biasanya pendiam,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:30.43,0:13:33.35,dialog,,0,0,0,,jadi aku senang dia punya teman.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:33.43,0:13:36.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak disangka ternyata\Ntemannya itu berengsek kayak kamu!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:38.11,0:13:42.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak mungkin pria berhati dingin itu\Nbisa berteman.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:44.65,0:13:47.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan membuatmu\Nmerasakan rasa sakit yang sama!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:47.49,0:13:48.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aduh!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:49.41,0:13:50.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu berlebihan! Jangan main kekerasan!
Dialogue: 10,0:13:50.78,0:13:53.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia sangat menyedihkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:54.71,0:13:56.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Waktu itu hujan deras,
Dialogue: 10,0:13:56.25,0:13:59.08,dialog,,0,0,0,,dia sendirian,\Njadi dia dikirim ke panti asuhan.
Dialogue: 10,0:13:59.50,0:14:01.84,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia kedinginan banget\Nsampai tidak bisa sebut namanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:02.59,0:14:05.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Setelah kami mandikan\Nbiar dia hangat,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:05.55,0:14:07.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,dia bilang dengan wajah kaget…
Dialogue: 10,0:14:08.30,0:14:09.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Ini hangat."
Dialogue: 10,0:14:09.89,0:14:12.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Seolah-olah itu mandi pertamanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:13.60,0:14:16.56,dialog,,0,0,0,,Habis itu, kami masakkan dia makanan.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:16.64,0:14:18.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lagi-lagi dia kaget.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:18.90,0:14:20.73,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Aku belum pernah makan yang begini."
Dialogue: 10,0:14:21.44,0:14:23.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaimana dia bisa bertahan sampai kini?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:23.48,0:14:26.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia bahkan tidak bisa memberi tahu kami\Nsiapa orang tuanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:26.49,0:14:29.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cuma anak yang tumbuh tanpa cinta\Nyang berakhir seperti itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:29.91,0:14:32.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ingin dia memulai hidup baru,
Dialogue: 10,0:14:32.49,0:14:34.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,jadi aku menamainya Satoru.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:34.91,0:14:37.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ingin dia dikelilingi oleh cinta…
Dialogue: 10,0:14:38.54,0:14:43.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf, tapi dia tidak seperti\Nyang kau pikirkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:43.30,0:14:44.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Percuma baik padanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:45.84,0:14:49.72,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya kau memang minta digebuki, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:14:49.80,0:14:52.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tunggu, takkan kubiarkan kau menyentuhnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:52.64,0:14:56.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sebagai orang yang berlatih karate, judo,\Ndan aikido, aku yang akan menghadapimu.
Dialogue: 10,0:14:58.19,0:15:00.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau pikir bisa mengalahkanku?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:00.90,0:15:03.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dengan tubuh kurusmu itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:05.44,0:15:06.78,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan lari!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:06.86,0:15:09.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak akan memaafkanmu\Nsampai kau minta maaf!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:10.70,0:15:11.53,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lewat sini!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:12.37,0:15:13.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fushi, berubahlah!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:14.24,0:15:15.83,dialog,,0,0,0,,Berubahlah menjadi apa pun!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:17.96,0:15:20.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa?\NKe mana dia pergi?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:20.71,0:15:22.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia pergi ke sana sendirian.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:23.88,0:15:24.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benarkah?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:24.80,0:15:26.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tidak bohong, kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:26.59,0:15:28.38,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lihat? Dia tidak ada di sini.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:28.47,0:15:29.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:15:30.63,0:15:31.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sial!
Dialogue: 10,0:15:32.01,0:15:33.97,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Kau takkan lolos dariku!\N- Aku tidak percaya ada gadis
Dialogue: 10,0:15:34.05,0:15:35.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,yang benar-benar melindunginya.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:35.56,0:15:38.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sepertinya dia beradaptasi dengan baik\Ndengan kehidupan manusia.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:39.94,0:15:42.44,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah! Aku berhasil melindungimu.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:43.69,0:15:45.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Entah apa yang terjadi,
Dialogue: 10,0:15:45.69,0:15:48.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi sebaiknya jangan bikin cewek marah.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:48.36,0:15:50.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau tidak,\Nitu hanya akan makin merepotkan.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:52.11,0:15:53.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Permisi.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:53.57,0:15:57.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami dari Klub Fotografi SD Minamoto.
Dialogue: 10,0:15:58.00,0:16:01.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maukah kalian menjadi model kami\Nuntuk beberapa foto?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:01.71,0:16:02.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Model?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:08.51,0:16:10.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Terima kasih banyak.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:10.80,0:16:12.76,dialog,,0,0,0,,Foto ini untukmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:12.84,0:16:15.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hubungi aku lagi saat kau\Ningin gunakan fotonya, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:15.55,0:16:16.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Baiklah.\N- Oke.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:16.81,0:16:18.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada apa, Fushi?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:18.10,0:16:19.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tampak bahagia.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:19.39,0:16:20.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau suka difoto?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:21.06,0:16:24.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku ingat sesuatu\Ntentang pemilik asli tubuh ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:25.40,0:16:27.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Namanya Mia.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:27.15,0:16:29.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Impiannya adalah menjadi model seni.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:29.36,0:16:31.74,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia meninggal sebelum impiannya terwujud.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:32.40,0:16:34.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini hanya foto,
Dialogue: 10,0:16:34.41,0:16:37.16,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi kau seperti mewujudkan\Nimpiannya, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:37.24,0:16:38.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kurasa juga begitu.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:39.08,0:16:40.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,Benar juga!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:40.29,0:16:41.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku juga bakal wujudkan\Nmimpi Oopa dan Uroy.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:42.00,0:16:44.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa? Ada lagi?
Dialogue: 10,0:16:44.50,0:16:47.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tentu, aku akan membantumu.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:51.05,0:16:55.14,dialog,,0,0,0,,Impian Uroy adalah\Nmemelihara banyak hewan.
Dialogue: 10,0:16:55.80,0:16:58.51,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada banyak hewan\Nyang belum pernah dilihat Uroy!
Dialogue: 10,0:16:58.60,0:17:01.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku yakin Uroy akan menyukainya.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:03.14,0:17:03.98,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lihat.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:04.52,0:17:06.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu Rasi Bintang Oniguma.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:06.19,0:17:09.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oopa tampak tertarik dengan matahari.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:10.07,0:17:13.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jika dia tahu ada bintang\Nyang lebih besar dan jauh dari matahari,
Dialogue: 10,0:17:13.90,0:17:15.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,dia pasti sangat terkejut.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:17.16,0:17:19.58,dialog,,0,0,0,,Maaf, ini sudah malam banget.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:20.08,0:17:22.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Makasih buat hari ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:22.70,0:17:25.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sangat senang\Nbisa ketemu kamu, Fushi.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:25.25,0:17:28.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tak disangka aku dulu pernah ingin mati.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:31.88,0:17:33.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sampai jumpa, Fushi.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:33.34,0:17:35.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Datanglah ke sekolah sesekali.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:41.27,0:17:43.68,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rasi Bintang Oniguma, ya?
Dialogue: 10,0:17:44.10,0:17:46.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Andai aku bisa memberi tahu March.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:47.10,0:17:49.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi aku belum bisa pulang.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:49.61,0:17:51.86,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak sampai aku menghabisi Mimori Nokker.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:52.28,0:17:53.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fushi!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:53.49,0:17:55.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ternyata kau di sana!
Dialogue: 10,0:17:55.45,0:17:56.45,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tonari.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:56.91,0:17:59.62,dialog,,0,0,0,,Semua orang khawatir\Nkarena kau belum pulang.
Dialogue: 10,0:17:59.70,0:18:02.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang kau lakukan dalam wujud Oopa?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:02.45,0:18:03.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku melihat bintang.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:04.54,0:18:05.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu Rasi Bintang Oniguma.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:06.71,0:18:08.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di mana?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:08.21,0:18:11.67,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bintang merah dan yang di sebelahnya…
Dialogue: 10,0:18:11.75,0:18:13.21,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tidak bisa melihatnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:13.30,0:18:15.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Atau bintang biru itu?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:15.76,0:18:17.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ini membangkitkan kenangan.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:17.63,0:18:20.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aroma manis bercampur\Naroma tanah dan minyak wangi.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:21.05,0:18:24.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,Andai Oopa masih hidup.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:24.81,0:18:26.64,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku sungguh berharap\Nbisa melihat bintang bersamanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:26.73,0:18:28.77,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku masih belum terbiasa\Nhanya punya satu mata.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:33.98,0:18:35.49,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fushi!
Dialogue: 10,0:18:36.74,0:18:38.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selamat tidur, Fushi.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:39.78,0:18:40.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selamat tidur.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:40.78,0:18:43.79,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi, kau bersama Mizuha hari ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:43.87,0:18:45.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, kami berkencan.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:46.54,0:18:48.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dalam bentuk Oopa?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:48.21,0:18:52.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya, Mizuha mengajakku\Nke tempat bernama Planetarium.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:52.17,0:18:54.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kita bisa lihat banyak bintang di sana.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:54.09,0:18:56.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oopa tertarik dengan matahari, bukan?
Dialogue: 10,0:18:56.51,0:18:58.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jadi aku ingin menunjukkan\Nbintang kepadanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:58.18,0:18:59.59,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami juga ke kebun binatang.
Dialogue: 10,0:18:59.68,0:19:02.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dalam bentuk Uroy,\Naku melihat hewan melalui matanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.01,0:19:03.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Selain itu,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:03.93,0:19:06.43,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku punya Mia sebagai model.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:06.52,0:19:08.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Lihat, ini foto. Bagus kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:08.39,0:19:09.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hentikan!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:10.15,0:19:11.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Di sana kau rupanya.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:12.27,0:19:14.57,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fushi! Tonari sudah memberitahumu, kan?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:14.65,0:19:16.19,dialog,,0,0,0,,Cepatlah kembali.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:17.95,0:19:19.66,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia tak memberitahumu?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:19.74,0:19:22.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bon ingin bicara denganmu.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:22.16,0:19:23.70,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kami tidak tahu kau di mana,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:23.78,0:19:26.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,jadi Tonari mengirim Ligard\Nuntuk mencarimu.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:28.00,0:19:29.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang terjadi?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:30.08,0:19:34.80,dialog,,0,0,0,,Orang ini... dia memanfaatkan teman-temanku\Ncuma buat urusan asmaranya.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:36.13,0:19:37.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa maksudmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:19:37.26,0:19:38.88,dialog,,0,0,0,,Mizuha cuma berniat baik...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:38.97,0:19:40.09,dialog,,0,0,0,,Diam! Aku tidak mau dengar!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:41.13,0:19:42.30,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dengar baik-baik.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:42.39,0:19:45.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dibandingkan denganmu,\Natau gadis bernama Mizuha itu,
Dialogue: 10,0:19:45.31,0:19:48.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oopa, Mia, dan Uroy...
Dialogue: 10,0:19:48.10,0:19:51.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,Merekalah yang paling kusayangi!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:51.90,0:19:53.61,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku menyayangi mereka lebih dari siapa pun!
Dialogue: 10,0:19:54.11,0:19:57.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Setelah Nokker mengambil alih\Ntubuh mereka, mereka mati.
Dialogue: 10,0:19:57.82,0:20:01.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sekuat apa pun mereka berjuang hidup,\Nnyawa mereka melayang begitu saja.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:02.16,0:20:03.07,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fushi.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:03.16,0:20:07.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kalau kau pikir kau yang menanggung\Nhidup mereka...
Dialogue: 10,0:20:07.70,0:20:11.37,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jangan berani-beraninya kau nodai\Nteman-temanku dengan hal sekotor itu!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:11.46,0:20:12.29,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tonari!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:13.42,0:20:14.71,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tonari!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:18.05,0:20:20.47,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fushi, aku hanya menebak,
Dialogue: 10,0:20:20.84,0:20:23.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,tapi Tonari tampak marah besar.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:23.09,0:20:24.39,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa kalian bertengkar?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:26.01,0:20:27.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:27.81,0:20:29.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ayo kembali dulu.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:29.93,0:20:31.89,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan cari cara agar Tonari tenang.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:31.98,0:20:33.94,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak! Aku tidak akan kembali!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:34.02,0:20:37.32,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kenapa tidak? Aku membuat mizutaki.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:37.40,0:20:39.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fushi, ada apa denganmu belakangan ini?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:39.44,0:20:40.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau tak pulang dan selalu pergi.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:41.07,0:20:41.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ada yang kau sembunyikan?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:42.07,0:20:44.28,dialog,,0,0,0,,Baiklah, Kak Gugu.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:44.36,0:20:46.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fushi lagi masa "itu" sekarang.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:46.12,0:20:46.95,dialog,,0,0,0,,"Itu"?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:47.03,0:20:48.91,dialog,,0,0,0,,Sesuatu yang selalu dialami\Nanak laki-laki.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:48.99,0:20:51.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia seperti kucing jantan\Nyang pernah kumiliki.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:51.62,0:20:54.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia kabur dari rumah saat musim kawin\Ndan tidak pernah kembali.
Dialogue: 10,0:20:55.29,0:20:58.13,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fushi lagi berahi?
Dialogue: 10,0:20:58.21,0:20:59.25,dialog,,0,0,0,,Ya!
Dialogue: 10,0:20:59.34,0:21:02.22,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau main sama Mizuha belakangan ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:02.30,0:21:05.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Itu sebabnya kau tak akur dengan Tonari\Ndan tak mau pulang.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:06.01,0:21:08.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,- Kita dikerjai.\N- Aku tak terlalu suka gadis itu.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:08.68,0:21:10.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tapi jika kau suka, aku akan dukung.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:10.60,0:21:11.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku yang akan bicara pada Tonari.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:11.93,0:21:12.85,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kau juga lakukan yang terbaik.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:13.44,0:21:16.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku akan menyuruh Pak Bon\Ndatang ke sekolah.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:17.11,0:21:20.36,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kak Gugu, ayo pulang.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:22.15,0:21:23.15,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku tak butuh.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:28.58,0:21:30.99,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku melakukan hal buruk kepada Tonari.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:31.79,0:21:35.50,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dahulu, aku tak bisa menyelamatkan Oopa\Ndan yang lainnya.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:36.04,0:21:38.34,dialog,,0,0,0,,Demi meredakan perasaan tidak berdaya itu,
Dialogue: 10,0:21:38.42,0:21:41.05,dialog,,0,0,0,,aku menggunakan tubuh mereka.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:42.13,0:21:43.92,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tidak mungkin
Dialogue: 10,0:21:44.01,0:21:47.01,dialog,,0,0,0,,Oopa dan Uroy bisa melihat\Napa yang kulihat.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:48.10,0:21:50.31,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hidup itu sangat sulit.
Dialogue: 10,0:21:54.23,0:21:57.52,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa minum bisa bikin tenang?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:01.19,0:22:03.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku bisa minum semauku\Ndalam wujud si Pemabuk.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:03.99,0:22:05.40,dialog,,0,0,0,,Rasanya enak.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:10.87,0:22:12.24,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kumohon…
Dialogue: 10,0:22:12.33,0:22:13.20,dialog,,0,0,0,,lihat ini!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:15.79,0:22:17.42,dialog,,0,0,0,,Fushi, kau baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:17.50,0:22:20.00,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa kau?\NApa yang kau lakukan pada Fushi?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:20.54,0:22:21.75,dialog,,0,0,0,,Aku
Dialogue: 10,0:22:22.55,0:22:24.46,dialog,,0,0,0,,hanya ingin dia melihat ini!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:25.09,0:22:26.55,dialog,,0,0,0,,Gumpalan rambut di tubuh itu!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:26.63,0:22:29.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Bagaikan jalur sutra hitam\Nyang berkilau di atas hamparan tanah putih!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:29.34,0:22:32.26,dialog,,0,0,0,,Belenggu yang mengikatnya!\NItulah karma kemanusiaan!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:32.35,0:22:36.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Antitesis dari segala noda kehidupan!
Dialogue: 10,0:22:36.19,0:22:38.10,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa sebenarnya kau?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:38.19,0:22:40.02,dialog,,0,0,0,,Hirotoshi.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:40.98,0:22:43.03,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia orang yang kutelepon.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:43.57,0:22:46.90,dialog,,0,0,0,,Dia mengintai di depan sekolah\Nbelakangan ini.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:46.99,0:22:50.41,dialog,,0,0,0,,Kudengar dia mencari Fushi,\Njadi aku tukaran kontak dengannya.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:50.49,0:22:53.12,dialog,,0,0,0,,Apa yang kau inginkan dariku, Mesum?
Dialogue: 10,0:22:54.08,0:22:56.54,dialog,,0,0,0,,Tolong selamatkan adikku.
Dialogue: 10,0:22:57.54,0:22:59.17,dialog,,0,0,0,,Menyelamatkan adikmu?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:32.55,0:24:34.60,dialog,,0,0,0,,Jiwa yang hancur
Dialogue: 10,0:24:34.68,0:24:36.81,dialog,,0,0,0,,dan tubuh yang hilang.
Dialogue: 10,0:24:37.85,0:24:40.93,dialog,,0,0,0,,Akankah tangisan kakaknya, Hirotoshi,
Dialogue: 10,0:24:41.44,0:24:44.06,dialog,,0,0,0,,mencapai Mimori?
Dialogue: 10,0:24:45.40,0:24:48.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,Siapa yang akan menang dalam pertarungan
Dialogue: 10,0:24:49.69,0:24:50.82,dialog,,0,0,0,,tengah malam ini?
